---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ProseSection from '../components/ProseSection.astro';
import CtaButton from '../components/CtaButton.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Welcome"
  description="A warm welcome to Toddler World, a loving, Montessori-inspired preschool in Srinagar for children aged 2–3."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="A note from us to you" title="Welcome to Toddler World" accent="sunny">
    <p>Thank you for your interest in giving your little one a joyful start.</p>
  </PageHero>

  <section class="section container">
    <ProseSection
      image="/images/Welcome/welcome.webp"
      alt="A happy child showing off her red and yellow painted hands"
      accent="green"
    >
      <p class="lead">
        A child is the most precious gift of our lives. Our priorities, hopes and dreams revolve
        around them, and as parents ourselves, we understand your wish to give them the very best.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Toddler World we've created the loving, caring environment your child deserves: a place
        just like home, that you can trust completely. We know in our hearts that there is no
        greater responsibility than giving a child the best possible start in life.
      </p>
      <p>
        Here, your child will delight in playing alongside other children and our warm, attentive
        staff, in an atmosphere that is nurturing and where their individuality is genuinely
        respected. We've built our curriculum with the whole child in mind, and our team works
        together every day to create rich, joyful classroom experiences that keep learning happy and
        balanced.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a low child-to-staff ratio, we're able to shape learning in a personal, meaningful way.
        We offer the best of everything: infrastructure, methodology, curriculum, a trained team
        and top-of-the-line learning equipment.
      </p>
      <p>
        And when you join Toddler World, we don't only enrol your child, we enrol you too. Our
        parent counselling workshops help you understand your child even better, so we can grow
        together.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong
          >We welcome you to Toddler World for a joyful journey towards love &amp; light.</strong
        >
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <CtaButton variant="sunny" href={site.integrations.enquiry} external
          >Enquire about a place</CtaButton
        >
        <CtaButton variant="ghost" href="/admissions">How admissions work</CtaButton>
      </div>
    </ProseSection>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
  }
</style>
